## Technical Requirements

### Technology Stack

**Backend:**
- .NET 10 (ASP.NET Core Web API)
- Entity Framework Core
- Azure SQL Database
- Azure App Service (transitioning to Docker/ACA)

**Frontend:**
- React 18 (TypeScript)
- Vite
- TanStack Query
- Tailwind CSS
- Radix UI

**Mobile:**
- .NET MAUI (iOS/Android)

**Infrastructure:**
- Azure B2C ? Entra External ID (migration Q2 2026)
- SendGrid (email)
- Google Maps API
- Sentry.io (monitoring)
- Azure Blob Storage
- Azure Key Vault
- GitHub Actions (CI/CD)

### Performance Requirements

- P95 API latency ? 300ms
- Crash-free sessions (mobile) ? 99.5%
- Page load time ? 3 seconds
- Map interactions smooth at 60fps
- Support 10,000+ concurrent users

### Security & Compliance

- HTTPS only
- JWT-based authentication
- Role-based authorization (User, Event Lead, Partner, Admin)
- COPPA compliance for minors (13+)
- Waiver management and legal retention
- PII protection
- Rate limiting on APIs
- Image moderation pipeline

### Accessibility

- WCAG 2.2 AA compliance
- Screen reader support
- Keyboard navigation
- Sufficient color contrast
- Semantic HTML

### Browser Support

**Web:**
- Chrome (latest 2 versions)
- Firefox (latest 2 versions)
- Safari (latest 2 versions)
- Edge (latest 2 versions)

**Mobile:**
- iOS 15+
- Android 8.0+

