## Appendix

### A. Glossary

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **Event** | A scheduled cleanup instance with public or private visibility |
| **Event Lead** | User who created and manages an event |
| **Volunteer** | Registered user (18+) or minor (13-17 with parental consent) |
| **Partner** | Organization providing services (hauling, supplies, etc.) |
| **Litter Report** | User-submitted report of litter locations |
| **Team** | User-created group with membership and collective impact tracking |
| **Waiver** | Liability waiver signed by participants before events |
| **Event Summary** | Post-event metrics (bags, attendees, duration) |
| **Pickup Location** | GPS-tagged location where bags are left for hauler |
| **Community** | City/region partnership (future feature) |

